          <p class="research-desc">Ongoing research on multimodal emotional intelligence using CLIP-based architectures for cross-modal sarcasm detection in text-image pairs. Combines vision-language models with fine-tuned RoBERTa for nuanced sentiment and irony classification in student feedback and social media data.</p>
